Package: sondage
Type: Package
Title: Survey Sampling Algorithms
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Ahmadou",
                  family = "Dicko",
	          email = "mail@ahmadoudicko.com",
		  comment = c(ORCID ="0000-0002-9654-7582"),
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:  Fast implementations of survey sampling algorithms for drawing
    samples from finite populations. Provides equal probability methods
    (simple random sampling, systematic, Bernoulli) and unequal probability
    methods (Brewer, maximum entropy/conditional Poisson, systematic PPS,
    Chromy's sequential PPS, Poisson, multinomial). Includes computation
    of first-order and joint inclusion probabilities. All functions return
    indices for easy subsetting. Based on algorithms from Tille (2006)
    "Sampling Algorithms" <doi:10.1007/0-387-34240-0>.
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
